e and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you what distinguishes the best of you from the worst of you? The best of you are those from whom good is expected and people are safe from their evil. The worst\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15142,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/19\/dua-new-clothing\/","url_meta":{"origin":20800,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Clothing: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for wearing new clothes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, wore a new garment he would name it, such as a turban, a shirt, or a cloak, and then he would say, \u201cO Allah, praise be to you that you have dressed me with it.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42020,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/07\/22\/abu-darda-we-know\/","url_meta":{"origin":20800,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Muslims: We know who is wicked or righteous","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Nufayr reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, used to say about people, \u201cWe know you better than a veterinarian knows his animals. We surely know the best of you from the worst of you. As for the best of you, goodness is expected from them\u2026","rel":"","co